strings: <voice_0x01000952><se_low>King of tricks: yes <hero> I thought you were missing!
<se_low>King of tricks: Darling, have you confessed recently?
<se_low>King of tricks: The journey has been fraught with risks... full of adventures that he sometimes regrets.
<voice_0x01000953><se_low>King of tricks: So let's go to the waterfall cave and find the crystal ball.
<voice_0x01000954><se_low>King of tricks: The press and I look for you. If you have any problems, please contact us.
<voice_0x01000956><se_low>King of tricks: Of course I do
<voice_0x01000957><se_low>King of tricks: Of course I want to go along with them. But I couldn't risk that in front of the media.
<voice_0x01000958><se_low>King of tricks: <hero> I think you can do the Crystal Ball quest without us. wait here
<voice_0x01000959><se_low>King of tricks: Pay attention to outside!
